<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">«إنّما سمّي الهوى لأنّه يهوي بصاحبه»</span> ) * <span class="c2">«٨»</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
